  "title": "Business Specialist",
  "description": "<p>About the role</p><p></p><p>What you'll be doing</p><p></p><p>1. Manage the company’s government relations and drive the implementation and cooperation of ongoing projects, including company registration, tax agency services, bank coordination, and business license formalities.</p><p>2. Handle business license applications for new projects, complete various certification procedures, visa processing, and oversee factory construction affairs.</p><p>3. Compile government application documents, follow up on the execution and acceptance of government cooperative projects, and assist in communication, coordination and reception with relevant government authorities.</p><p>4. Timely collect, organize, analyze and report industry-related policy updates and information.</p><p>5. Be responsible for enterprise qualification certification and related matters.</p><p>6. Undertake business receptions and accompany factory audits.</p><p></p><p>Job Requirements</p><p></p><p>1. Full-time bachelor’s degree or above, with 1+ years of relevant work experience.</p><p>2. 1 years of business-related experience.</p><p></p><p>What we offer</p><p></p><p>At GOLDEN PHOENIX SOLAR ENERGY PTE.LTD.', we are committed to providing a supportive and inclusive work environment where employees can thrive. We offer competitive salaries, comprehensive benefits, and opportunities for professional development. Our focus on work-life balance and employee wellbeing ensures that our team members are empowered to bring their best selves to work every day.</p><p></p><p>About us</p><p></p><p>GOLDEN PHOENIX SOLAR ENERGY PTE.LTD.' is a leading provider of renewable energy solutions in the region. Our mission is to drive the transition towards a sustainable future by delivering innovative solar energy products and services. With a team of highly skilled professionals and a commitment to excellence, we have established a strong reputation in the industry and are poised for continued growth.</p><p></p><p>Apply now to join our dynamic team!</p>",
